name: Genesis World Art Day
description: This is the first World Art Day - thus Genesis - and I'm proud to be part of it. Hic et Nunc is an amazing platform uniting artists from all over the world (I'm from Germany) - and creating the opportunity of World Art Day for a good cause. Technology changing the world for the better - creativity rocks! GIF with 1.984 px and 26 frames. http://qizz.io
